title: Person of Interest Season 5 First Look (HD)
author: televisionpromosdb
comment: please don't end this, this is the only show keeps me excited.

The sneak peak itself was great but Root once again being the show stealer and sending this stuff to so many levels of awesome.  Love the " You can just call me Root bitch " line. Kind of a bad ass play on here original classic introduction line from season 1. Throw backs!
six seasons and a movie! stomps foot
This deserved a full final season.
